messages.message:
Yeah, the blocker on this is that AI Hub users shouldn’t have to be exposed to endpoints specific to IB platform, which aren’t useful in AI Hub, so we await fixes from eng.

edited for clarity

I’m unsure how we get API work prioritized; it seems important to customers. Any thoughts @margaret.tomaszczuk? It seems like there’s a disconnect around the priority of API work given the number of customer requests.
@jack.robbins do you happen to have context on this one? Otherwise happy to take a look.

The nuance here is that ST customers can use the old IB platform APIs _with limited caveats_, but there are gaps if MT customers need use these APIs.

We've had https://instabase.atlassian.net/browse/EPD-3465 on the backlog for some time, but since we're able to unstick ST customers, which are usually the ones that need these APIs, it hasn't been as much of a fire.
